All right.  I approved finding Vector Sigma on Cybertron.  Bringing it here 
is something else entirely.  So Kyle, your post is void, however, LN although 
it's nice to know why a ship is coming and where it's coming from it isn't 
mandatory.  As for acting on my decision alone, the only reason I approved 
his request is because, I think there's precedent for Vector Sigma and the 
Organic Core, but I'll check that when I have some free time.

--part1_10e.921e5f3.294a65d6_boundary
